at the public defender's office.

1083
01:10:33,859 --> 01:10:35,777
He wanted me to do well.

1084
01:10:37,779 --> 01:10:41,200
We had a plan until you came along
and messed everything up.

1085
01:10:41,700 --> 01:10:44,828
l wish l had been able to take care
of my little sister.

1086
01:10:45,704 --> 01:10:46,830
l mean...

1087
01:10:46,997 --> 01:10:48,790
...family's family, right?

1088
