Henri, l'm sorry you're here.

1089
01:10:54,463 --> 01:10:57,049
This here's paradise
compared to my last home.

1090
01:10:59,301 --> 01:11:02,513
How about the case?
Do you want to talk about it a bit now?

1091
01:11:02,638 --> 01:11:04,431
You never give up, do you?

1092
01:11:08,727 --> 01:11:10,062
How about the Redskins?

1093
01:11:10,145 --> 01:11:13,315
How do you think they'll do
against the Yankees this year?

1094
01:11:14,483 --> 01:11:16,527
Redskins are a football team.

1095
01:11:16,652 --> 01:11:18,654
Yankees are a baseball team.

1096
01:11:19,238 --> 01:11:22,741
Personally, l think the Redskins
will kick the shit out of them.

1097
01:11:25,410 --> 01:11:27,037
Henri, l'm trying.

1098
01:11:28,247 --> 01:11:29,289
l know.

1099
01:11:29,540 --> 01:11:32,543
This is going to be
a private conversation, Byron.

1100
01:11:33,168 --> 01:11:35,337
lt never took place, all right?

1101
01:11:35,629 --> 01:11:38,340
-ls that all right, Thurgood?
-l suggested it.

1102
01:11:39,424 --> 01:11:42,886
That brother of yours is making
quite a little name for himself.

1103
01:11:43,011 --> 01:11:44,972
We even heard his name in Washington.

1104
01:11:45,055 --> 01:11:47,307
My brother has resigned from the case.

1105
01:11:47,474 --> 01:11:50,227
Well, he was hired back again last night.

1106
01:11:50,519 --> 01:11:52,646
What do you mean he was hired back?

1107
01:11:56,775 --> 01:12:00,028
Your work here has been stellar.
l'd hate to see anything--

1108
01:12:00,112 --> 01:12:01,864
What exactly are you saying?

1109
01:12:01,947 --> 01:12:04,825
This administration is not going to allow...

1110
01:12:04,908 --> 01:12:07,995
...public attention to be diverted
from all the good it's done...

1111
01:12:08,078 --> 01:12:11,039
...by some kind of a witch hunt
in the Justice Department.

1112
01:12:11,123 --> 01:12:13,584
l'm just telling you what the score is.

1113
01:12:13,834 --> 01:12:15,961
lt's up to you to take care of him.

1114
01:12:18,380 --> 01:12:21,258
Why would J. Edgar Hoover care
about what happens to Henri?

1115
01:12:21,341 --> 01:12:24,761
Grow up. He doesn't care
about what happens to Henri.

1116
01:12:24,845 --> 01:12:26,305
He cares about...

1117
01:12:26,889 --> 01:12:29,141
...Alcatraz, the Justice Department...

1118
01:12:30,100 --> 01:12:31,852
...Humson, the Administration.

1119
01:12:31,935 --> 01:12:34,563
He can't have some kid from the P.D.'s--

1120
01:12:34,646 --> 01:12:36,732
l'm not a public defender anymore.

1121
01:12:37,107 --> 01:12:38,734
You know the point.

1122
01:12:39,151 --> 01:12:43,197
The point is l'm trying to do what's right.
l'm talking about justice here.

1123
01:12:43,363 --> 01:12:46,575
You're disgusted about what happened
on Alcatraz. So am l.

1124
01:12:47,618 --> 01:12:50,245
But if you tear the whole system down...

1125
01:12:50,495 --> 01:12:52,664
...what does that say about America?

1126
01:12:53,165 --> 01:12:54,333
We're wrong.

1127
01:12:55,626 --> 01:12:57,085
We can't be wrong.

1128
01:12:57,836 --> 01:13:02,257
The world is fighting right now
to preserve our system, our way of life.

1129
01:13:02,841 --> 01:13:04,801
You can't attack it blindly.

1130
01:13:04,968 --> 01:13:08,430
We're talking about one man here.
lt's not that big of a deal.

1131
01:13:09,640 --> 01:13:11,934
-You're under surveillance.
-What?

1132
01:13:12,809 --> 01:13:16,396
Everyone is watching you.
Tell me how you plan to continue.

1133
01:13:17,856 --> 01:13:21,944
You have to realize, no one will talk.
Everyone has been gotten to.

1134
01:13:23,654 --> 01:13:25,030
l have somebody.

1135
01:13:25,781 --> 01:13:26,740
Who?

1136
01:13:28,909 --> 01:13:30,285
l can't tell you.

1137
01:13:31,495 --> 01:13:33,163
So, now you don't trust me?

1138
01:13:33,288 --> 01:13:35,332
You're my brother. l love you.

1139
01:13:35,832 --> 01:13:37,417
l need your help.

1140
01:13:44,967 --> 01:13:47,052
l can't do it. l'm sorry...

1141
01:13:47,469 --> 01:13:48,720
...but l can't.

1142
01:13:50,472 --> 01:13:51,515
l can't.

1143
01:14:04,236 --> 01:14:06,613
James, as a consolation...

1144
01:14:07,406 --> 01:14:10,033
...please don't put Humson on the stand.

1145
01:14:11,785 --> 01:14:12,744
Why?

1146
01:14:14,162 --> 01:14:16,123
Humson was handpicked by Hoover.

1147
01:14:16,206 --> 01:14:20,085
lt would save a lot of embarrassment
if you were to avoid Humson.

1148
01:14:22,921 --> 01:14:24,381
l'll think about it.

1149
01:14:26,175 --> 01:14:27,217
Thank you.

1150
01:14:30,721 --> 01:14:32,181
l'm sorry, Byron.

1151
01:14:47,905 --> 01:14:48,989
Yeah?

1152
01:14:50,490 --> 01:14:51,909
<i>Mr. Stamphill?</i>

1153
01:14:52,075 --> 01:14:53,702
<i>This is James Stamphill.</i>

1154
01:14:53,911 --> 01:14:56,914
<i>This is Derek Simpson.
Remember we talked before?</i>

1155
01:14:56,955 --> 01:15:00,626
<i>Right. Of course, I remember.
Have you made your decision?</i>

1156
01:15:01,960 --> 01:15:06,590
<i>I've been thinking about what we were
talking about and I'd like to be a witness.</i>

1157
01:15:07,216 --> 01:15:08,258
<i>Wonderful.</i>

1158
01:15:08,634 --> 01:15:11,470
<i>You do understand you must testify
in court under oath...</i>

1159
01:15:11,553 --> 01:15:14,056
<i>...about the brutality you witnessed
at Alcatraz.</i>

1160
01:15:14,181 --> 01:15:15,307
<i>I know that.</i>

1161
01:15:15,432 --> 01:15:17,935
<i>Particularly in reference to Henri Young.</i>

1162
01:15:18,936 --> 01:15:20,646
<i>I know some things.</i>

1163
01:15:21,688 --> 01:15:23,690
<i>Do you hold any sort of grudge...</i>

1164
01:15:23,815 --> 01:15:26,276
<i>...against Warden Humson
or Associate Warden Glenn?</i>

1165
01:15:26,360 --> 01:15:27,361
<i>No.</i>

1166
01:15:28,487 --> 01:15:30,781
<i>I'll come over and we can speak in person.</i>

1167
01:15:30,906 --> 01:15:32,908
<i>Yes. I'm in Chinatown.</i>

1168
01:15:33,909 --> 01:15:37,246
<i>It's an alley called Scotland Court.
The number there is 964.</i>

1169
01:15:49,299 --> 01:15:51,260
Mr. Simpson, are you in here?

1170
01:15:55,264 --> 01:15:57,474
Mr. Simpson, are you all right?

1171
01:16:10,112 --> 01:16:11,446
You all right?

1172
01:16:12,823 --> 01:16:14,950
Do you still want to be a witness?

1173
01:16:27,880 --> 01:16:28,839
Who's she?

1174
01:16:29,464 --> 01:16:31,300
She's a court reporter.

1175
01:16:31,675 --> 01:16:33,177
What happened to your face?

1176
01:16:33,302 --> 01:16:36,180
My face had a little accident this morning.

1177
01:16:36,263 --> 01:16:38,473
We need to get one more deposition...

1178
01:16:38,807 --> 01:16:39,433
No.

1179
01:16:39,516 --> 01:16:42,978
