Your eye, your leg....

1180
01:16:44,521 --> 01:16:47,774
Remember when you told me
you'd never been with a woman before?

1181
01:16:47,858 --> 01:16:50,527
Henri, this is Blanche.
Blanche, this is Henri.

1182
01:16:50,819 --> 01:16:52,112
Nice to meet you.

1183
01:16:52,196 --> 01:16:55,908
You got about four minutes before
the next guard arrives, so you gotta hurry.

1184
01:16:56,033 --> 01:17:00,078
l can't leave the room. l'm just going
to be over here. l'll turn my back.

1185
01:17:00,829 --> 01:17:02,372
We can get acquainted.

1186
01:17:09,004 --> 01:17:11,423
Come on, honey, we don't have all night.

1187
01:17:12,508 --> 01:17:13,717
Thanks, Jim.

1188
01:17:14,259 --> 01:17:15,761
You're a good friend.

1189
01:17:17,429 --> 01:17:18,514
Oh, boy.

1190
01:17:26,939 --> 01:17:28,565
Thanks. Hi, Charlie.

1191
01:17:30,234 --> 01:17:31,360
What's the story?

1192
01:17:31,485 --> 01:17:34,446
The attorney and a reporter inside
with the prisoner.

1193
01:17:34,571 --> 01:17:37,824
